{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e16b344512","title":"复刘少奇电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"401ada3785","index":0,"year":1941,"month":10,"day":11,"articleId":"e16b344512"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5c6d2cb919","type":"paragraph","text":"复刘少奇电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"e16b344512"},{"id":"9366ab2662","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年10月11日）来电蒸。（一）即来延安，既于自前工作不利，自宜缓期。（二七大大约还需等半年才开，甚望你能到会，请与陈、姚”各同志面，能否在两三个月内帮助他们解决一些问题，两三月后动身来延参加七大，七大后你在延安休养，即在延安指挥华中。（三）依国内外大局看，蒋及国民党不会投降，亦不可能大举“则共”，华中我军主要是对敌伪分散作战，你来延安指挥华中，似对华中工作不会有大损失，面你的身体得到休养，则有大益。以上请考虑见告。[1]这是毛泽东复刘少奇电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"e16b344512"}],"page":{"id":"829bd59d30","publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"e16b344512","start":255,"end":255}}}},"__N_SSG":true}